3.6. Non-Waiver of Enforcement Rights: The Licensor’s decision to prioritize platform-level copyright strikes (Article 3.2) over immediate judicial litigation does not constitute a waiver of copyright ownership. The Licensor retains the full right to report violations to national intellectual property authorities or initiate formal legal/criminal proceedings at any time.

